      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been garage-kept and pampered since day one. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
