    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been professionally overhauled. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis is impeccable, with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings to preserve the factory-tuned kinematics. Every mechanical component operates with surgical precision, from the atmospheric induction note to the firm, fade-free braking performance. A truly turn-key example for the collector demanding an uncompromised analog driving experience.",
