      "description": "This vehicle is a genuine time capsule, meticulously preserved in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or stone chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is entirely free of sun-fading or micro-scratches. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented history. From the untouched alloy wheels to the crisp, factory-fresh scent of the interior, this is an investment-grade example that satisfies the most demanding standards of perfection.",
