    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera, presenting in concours-level condition. This 996.2 generation features the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical provenance is impeccable, including a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a recent bore-scope inspection confirming zero scoring. Performance is sharpened by a factory-optioned limited-slip differential and a precision-tuned suspension with Bilstein dampers. The throttle response remains razor-sharp, and the VarioCam Plus system provides a seamless power band from 4,000 RPM to redline. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is current, ensuring a visceral, analog driving experience without compromise. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning purist.",
